<p class="CxSpMiddle" dir="RTL" style="margin-right:-42.6pt; text-align:justify"><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="AR-SA" style="font-size:14.0pt"><span arabic="" simplified="" style="font-family:">4.</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span lang="AR-SA" style="font-size:14.0pt"><span arabic="" simplified="" style="font-family:">بيان حياة جامعية.</span></span></span></span></p>

